Anyone else get a letter from New York Life stating their Jan & Feb premiums haven't been paid when they have EFT? my elderly mother did--and this upset her because it said her policy (of 40+ years) would be cancelled. She called in and apparently this happened to many people even though they paid. The rep didn't apologize to her & said a letter is going out to everyone affected. Feb hasn't arrived yet--isn't that red flag? How can New York Life neglect to monitor the communications it sends out? It should have been posted on the website or here that this error occurred. The company you keep shouldn't hide the truth--transparency please.
